<<elseif $companion_type == "warrior">>
    The warrior's hand rests instinctively on their weapon, trained reflexes already sensing danger.
    
    Warrior: "I've faced many enemies, but this... this feels wrong. Like the world itself is wounded."
<<elseif $companion_type == "guide">>
    The guide surveys the terrain with experienced eyes, but uncertainty clouds their usually confident demeanor.
    
