title: Examine the surroundings
tags: world_intro
---
The landscape stretches before you in hexagonal patches, each tile of reality distinct yet unnaturally connected.

Grasslands fade abruptly into dense forests. Mountains rise without foothills. Swamps border deserts in defiance of nature's laws.

<<set $dread_level += 2>>

This is not a world that grew naturally. This is a world that was... assembled.

