Through the strange patchwork landscape, a structure rises from what appears to be a grassland tile.

Even from this distance, you can tell it's wrong. The proportions are subtly off, the shadows fall in directions that don't match the sun.

<<set $dread_level += 1>>

Your companion follows your gaze: "Should we... investigate?"

