title: Comfort your companion
tags: companion_care
---
You place a gentle hand on your companion's shoulder, feeling them trembling slightly.

"It's alright," you say, though you're not sure you believe it yourself. "We'll take this one step at a time."

<<set $companion_stress -= 8>>
<<set $companion_trust += 5>>

Your companion takes a deep breath, steadying themselves: "Thank you. I... I needed that. This place gets inside your head so quickly."

The simple act of human connection feels precious here, a reminder of warmth in a cold world.

